}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "2976300501" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. :The (two) RAM chips appear to be '''M12L64164A-7T'''s for 16MB total..
This device has an additional model of RSVLC-0702.
Default settings (including the SSIDs) are per the '''HP''''s manual. :The manual states that the 802.11 radios are disabled by default.
